name: Huckleberry Inu
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: Huckleberry Inu is here to unite the whole meme crypto world, inspired by the top memes Doge, Shiba Inu, Baby Doge, Dogelon, Saitama and Cult. We are a versatile community driven project that will transcend space & time with a roadmap focused on entertainment & utility. HKBY's uilitity is related to both web2 and web3 games, NFTs, Dapps like Huckleswap and more. Our community is constantly growing and talented people are joining us, therefore it is sure that the utility of our HKBY will be expanded. Huckleberry Inu was created by a group of crypto enthusiasts & lovers of old school cartoons. Join our fun filled community for lots of memes, contests, giveaways & much more.
